NAME
clamscan-notify.sh - Scan stdin with clamav in foreground or by daemon
SYNOPSIS
clamscan-notify.sh [OPTION]
DESCRIPTION
The script uses clamav (foreground or daemon) to scan stdin for viruses.
OPTIONS
-d, --daemon  Use the clam av daemon instead of foreground process

-h, --help  prints usage information.

-V, --version  prints version information
EXIT STATUS
0 - Success

1 - General failure

64 - Error in command line

